                            	  5649: LAB_CORD
00:00002982 176B0595059E    	  5650: 	move.b	FAC1_s(a3),FAC_sc(a3)	* copy as sign compare for TAN
00:00002988 DC86            	  5651: 	ADD.l		d6,d6				* shift 0.5 bit into carry
00:0000298A 6406            	  5652: 	BCC.s		LAB_LTPF			* branch if less than 0.5
